{"tid":1301862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘海富連儂牆要人！！！","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:31:49.000Z","uid":146673,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c5a3253cbf6ea3951cfb6d83692386fb4e9135","tid":1301862,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"[推!] 金鐘海富連儂牆！將絕食者精神發揚光大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301523</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推番自己個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日一班絕食者會開記者會！<br />\n我哋要再次把握機會推上國際，香港政府漠視民意！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 集中喺海富對出嘅連儂牆啦<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n唔好辜負一班絕食者心血，特別係陳伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當陳伯用生命作賭注嘅時候，唔休息都要諗對策同記者溝通<br />\n我哋暫時就唔好再對其他連儂牆打飛機先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果聽日班記者見到附近有咁大幅連儂牆，呢班絕食者有可能會引發更高關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋要證明俾人睇，我哋香港人係高汁架，同呢個冷血政府形成強烈對比！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家經開金鐘，幫下手擴大連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">記者會詳情：<br />\n日期： 2019年7 月10日 (星期三)<br />\n時間： 晚上七點半<br />\n地點： 金鐘海富地鐵站出口<br />\n發言人： 好鄰舍北區教會傳道人陳凱興、絕食人士陳伯</span>"},{"pid":"94f3ab84ca1d0f12fae70239579174027fab9f81","tid":1301862,"uid":34515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/