. 成立獨立監警機構 <br />\n追究所有反送中示威入面所有違規警員<br />\n<br />\n2. 爭取全民直選立法、行政長官<br />\n取消功能組別 由下個立法會/行政長官選舉開始<br />\n<br />\n3. 特赦/大赦所有六月九至七月七所有示威者檢控</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家參與討論👇👇👇<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求其實有兩條都係冇意義<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301113\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301113</a>"},{"pid":"6eb8f68938fbc0ebca9aa90aa140febcd8a24c93","tid":1301862,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a61490f25511c80f623cf5ad2654c47871d46d8","tid":1301862,"uid":42852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"希望陳伯冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d14dc660f7fb3f9c969d82cd9090adbd999f10","tid":1301862,"uid":274658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"陳伯身體點呀 我最驚係佢頂唔住"},{"pid":"e19247ecb35c16ece67a44ff6291e471c9197091","tid":1301862,"uid":146673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7a61490f25511c80f623cf5ad2654c47871d46d8","tid":1301862,"uid":42852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"希望陳伯冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"陳伯暫時安全，但都缺乏營養，聲沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到11點半，有2個人坐喺佢隔睇住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我哋依加要做嘅，係俾多啲支持鼓勵佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a5f8bffcd3e0f55a772c5c120814212c2f095d","tid":1301862,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:13.000Z","msg":"【713 光復上水UPDATE】<br />\n<br />\n今晚我們同接近20位警方人員係上水警署開會商討遊行路線及安排，由於警方評估後認為今次遊行將會有大量參與者，而原集合地點 &ndash; 「上水花園第一號」無法容納參與遊行的人士，故此建議我們將遊行集合地點改為面積更大的 -「北區運動場籃球場」，以便容納更加多的參與人士。<br />\n<br />\n在跟警方商討後，我們決定接納警方的建議，將集合地點改為「北區運動場籃球場」，敬請各位留意。<br />\n<br />\n「不反對通知書」仍在批核階段，相信我們於短期內會收到警方就是次遊行發出的「不反對通知書」。如有進一步的消息，我們會盡快向各位公佈。<br />\n<br />\n消息發佈:<br />\n請留意本專頁 或<br />\nTelegram Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Assemble713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAssemble713&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=f298d1fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Assemble713</a><br />\n<br />\n招募義工:<br />\n由於我們將會進行街站宣傳，另外，警方要求我們安排糾察或義工沿途維持秩序，如有意成為義工，請經INBOX聯絡我們 或<br />\n加入Telegram 群組:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=0f51eed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug</a>"},{"pid":"3b0a40de7ad2be189bcb3f37f3b4c15a1960835d","tid":1301862,"uid":146673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0479e7ee1c7807f831720fc8da2075c5fdd1ec","tid":1301862,"uid":42852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e19247ecb35c16ece67a44ff6291e471c9197091","tid":1301862,"uid":146673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7a61490f25511c80f623cf5ad2654c47871d46d8","tid":1301862,"uid":42852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:05:27.000Z","msg":"希望陳伯冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"陳伯暫時安全，但都缺乏營養，聲沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl